  "body": "# Problem\n\nBack button breaks Accounts screen on Androids. There are several cases here, which will be logged as separate issues:\n\n2. Case two: Welcome screen is shown when user taps Back device button when being on Get yourself a key first screen. Looks like all accounts are gone (which is not true)\n\nSteps:\n1. open status and create account\n2. logout\n3. tap Generate new key\n4. tap build-in `<` button or device Back button\n\nActual result: welcome screen is shown\nExpected result: user should be redirected to previous screen (list of accounts)\n\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/62869464-9650ed80-bd20-11e9-9221-ec57ed47e15b.png)\n\n\nVideo: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1pIrRiA2Vygp8-1LDJy-af9aTn5vaLqGF",
